"><circle cx=\"8\" cy=\"8\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#fece34\"/><circle cx=\"8\" cy=\"2\" r=\"1.5\" fill=\"#61dafb\"/><circle cx=\"14\" cy=\"8\" r=\"1.2\" fill=\"#a57b0a\"/><circle cx=\"8\" cy=\"14\" r=\"1.2\" fill=\"#61dafb\"/><circle cx=\"2\" cy=\"8\" r=\"1.2\" fill=\"#a57b0a\"/></svg><svg class=\"sparkle\" style=\"top: 60px; left: 60px; width: 10px; height: 10px; animation-delay: 0.5s;\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\"><circle cx=\"5\" cy=\"5\" r=\"2\" fill=\"#fece34\"/></svg><svg class=\"sparkle\" style=\"top: 10px; left: 60px; width: 8px; height: 8px; animation-delay: 1s;\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 8\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"1.5\" fill=\"#61dafb\"/></svg><svg class=\"sparkle\" style=\"top: 70px; left: 20px; width: 7px; height: 7px; animation-delay: 0.8s;\" viewBox=\"0 0 7 7\"><circle cx=\"3.5\" cy=\"3.5\" r=\"1\" fill=\"#a57b0a\"/></svg><img class=\"logo\" src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/h4LrqyWK/Screenshot-2025-12-02-at-7-23-24-AM-removebg-preview.png\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" alt=\"LxParking Logo\"/></div><h2>OTP Verification</h2><div class=\"greeting\">Hi {employee},</div><div>Your verification OTP is shown below.</div><div class=\"otp-box\">{otp}</div><div>This OTP is valid for <b>{expiryMinutes} minutes</b>.</div><div class=\"footer\">Keep this OTP confidential.<br>If you didn’t request it, please ignore this email.<br><br>Best regards,<br>LxParking Team</div></div></body></html>\n";
